*[[Metropolitan Museum of Art]], New York
*[[San Diego Museum of Art]]<ref name=les/>
*[[Eiteljorg Museum of American Indians and Western Art]], Indianapolis
*[[National Museum of the American Indian]], Washington, DC
*[[Gilcrease Museum]], Tulsa, Oklahoma
*[[Montclair Art Museum]], New Jersey
*[[Cherokee Heritage Center]], Park Hill, Oklahoma

==Quote==
''I do not see my paintings as landscapes, per se, but rather as paintings that describe two kins of perception of the earth. One view is visual and fleeting and the other is abstract and everlasting. Thse paintings are my attempt to express the mythically inexpressible and to unify the present with eternity.''<ref name=big/>

